            <div type="translation">
                <p>Repent, for the kingdom of heaven is at hand.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Poor condition. The words μετανοεῖτε, βασιλεία are misspelled. Accents and breathings with errors. The text ends in two lines of four crosses each. The inscription is referred to the preaching of the Saint John the Forerunner and is an exerpt of Matthew's gospel (Matt. 3:2). </p>
            </div>
